data.description: Nice straight-thru Row home features large Living Room w/ art fireplace; formal Dining Room with large closet; hardwood flooring throughout. Remodeled Eat-in Kitchen, new GD, new flooring, entrance to separate cooking area. Master Bedroom with large closet. Two other nice sized Bedrooms. Newer remodeled Hall Bathroom (2021): newer fixtures, new skylight.  Newer Finished Rec Room (2022). Newer Powder Room (5-22), Exit to laundry room and rear fenced driveway. Newer roof (2021) warranty transferrable. Newer windows t/o (2018), Newer 50-gallon Hot water heater (2021), replaced garage door opener, new security screen door and front steel door. New 200-amp service. Sewer line was replaced (2021). Newer CROWN boiler (2017). New fence in front. (flooring is real hardwood-not laminate). Has semi-enclosed front patio. House qualifies for 1st time Buyers programs. Qualified buyers can get two programs, for up to $20K towards misc settlement charges and down deposit monies.
